{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"agent"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Spooktacular guest agent runs inside the VM and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"communicates with the host over a VirtIO socket (vsock) —"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a direct channel that works without networking. The host"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pushes the script to the agent, which executes it and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"streams output back."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Best for:"}]},{"type":"text","text":" VMs created from Spooktacular’s official OCI"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"images, which include the agent pre-installed. Fastest"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provisioning, works with isolated (no-network) VMs."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Requires:"}]},{"type":"text","text":" The Spooktacular guest agent installed in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the VM. Included in all "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ghcr.io\/spooktacular\/"},{"type":"text","text":" images."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/provisioningmode\/agent"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"agent"}],"symbolKind":"case","modules":[{"name":"SpooktacularKit"}],"externalID":"s:15SpooktacularKit16Provi